{"tid":316956,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6職員周家上班隨時候命","createTime":"2017-07-11T06:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T06:15:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2001ef745bec071a9cf4e13dc06164dc0db4fea3","tid":316956,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T06:14:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20085677&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20085677%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170711&d=RWfcpYAj8BCAA7VXPsDiDGxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=66ed1d3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20085677%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170711&h=de82a776\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20085677&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170711</a><br />\n<br />\n6職員周家上班隨時候命<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n周向榮<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】證人胡詠欣於2012年1月起在周向榮家中任夜更文員一年半。她指當初報章招聘廣告沒註明僱主和工作地點，面試時職員稱是幫一名退休商人打理日常事務。至於為何要在周向榮麒麟閣家中上班，職員解釋周做事很急，「一諗到就要做，所以安排一隊人喺佢身邊」。<br />\n據胡憶述，周和太太、父親、姊姊、5名子女居於麒麟閣，有多於4名女傭。她的辦公室是約100呎大、連廁所的房間，有4排座位，其中一排是周和太太所用。胡和另外5名職員分早午晚3更，由早上10時運作至凌晨1時，設夜更因需等門市收工後提交營業數據作整理。<br />\n胡指2012年9月底至10月初案發時，單位有僭建問題需裝修，辦公室搬到鄰近住宅碧廬。當時周胞姊周欣欣住在碧廬，終日顯得疲累寡言，周較多留家照料胞姊，胡知道她患癌並曾接受DR的治療。早前證供指她亦做了涉案療程，與其他事主感染同一種細菌。<br />\n■記者勞東來<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n周向榮：人生無常 盡量搵錢<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;8小時前"},{"pid":"2bf09465bfed18769391673ddf0b1c10bad200fa","tid":316956,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T06:15:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170711/large/a0805a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170711%2Flarge%2Fa0805a.gif&h=98f71d71&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}